-- Regency Energy Partners to buy PVR Partners for $5.6 billion
-- 
-- Thu Oct 10, 2013 8:23am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/10/10/us-pvrpartnerslp-offer-regencyenergy-idUSBRE9990FL20131010

 

 (Reuters) - Natural gas pipeline operator Regency Energy Partners LP ( RGP.N ) will buy rival PVR Partners LP ( PVR.N ) for $5.6 billion, including debt, giving it a foothold in the prolific Marcellus and Utica shale fields. 
 The deal includes the assumption of $1.8 billion in debt, the companies said. (Reporting by Swetha Gopinath in Bangalore; Editing by Don Sebastian)